      predefined values, it is possible to allocate additional values for 
      custom attributes using <function class="Pango">attr_type_register</function>.
      The predefined values are given below. 
      The type of structure used to store the attribute is listed in 
      parentheses after the description.
   </para>
  </desc>
  <enumoption>
   <value>0</value>
   <optionname>Pango::ATTR_INVALID</optionname>
   <shortdesc>
    
   </shortdesc>
  </enumoption>
  <enumoption>
   <value>1</value>
   <optionname>Pango::ATTR_LANGUAGE</optionname>
   <shortdesc>
       Language (PangoAttrLanguage).
   </shortdesc>
  </enumoption>
  <enumoption>
